  • save_results

    Save model results to csvs

output_functions.save_results(name, years, results_list, results)¶

Save model results.

Model results are saved in a series of structure csv files. The backend of the model frontend will read these csvs.

Parameters

  • name (str) – Name of model run, and specification file read

  • years (tuple (int, int)) – Bookend years of solution

  • results_list (list of str) – List of variable names, specifying results to print

  • results (dictionary of numpy arrays) – Dictionary containing all model results

Returns

Detailed description

Return type

None

Notes

This function is under construction.
